Charming Mzansi tennis star Kevin Anderson is in the final at Wimbledon after a historic semifinal on Friday. In a six hour, 36 minutes epic match, one of the longest-ever at the London Lawn Tennis Club, Anderson's endurance was optimally tested by his opponent American John Isner. You've made us proud and are rooting for you, charmza, to win the final today. Well done, Kevin.